runon landings the officials said its top speed during the 
tests was limited to 20 knots less than 25 mph 
the aircraft combines the operational capabilities of a 
helicopter with those of a fixedwind turboprop with its engines 
and proprotors vertical the v22 takes off hovers and lands like 
a helicopter 
with its proprotors in forward position the osprey would become 
a fast fuelefficient highaltitude turboprop airplane capable of 
reaching speeds of more than 345 mph 
