the us military the ability to develop new missions and tactics 
that cannot be accomplished by any existing helicopter or airplane 
six flighttest prototypes are being built by bell helicopter 
textron inc in fort worth and boeing helicopters of philadelphia a 
division of boeing co under a 18 billion fullscale development 
contract issued by the us naval air systems command 
the versatile osprey is the first modern weapons system designed 
from conception to meet requirements of all four us armed 
