closed friday at 33 in new york stock exchange composite trading 
universal executives contend a takeover would damage the 
companys longterm growth including its ability to invest in 
research and development of new products 
universal based in milwaukee is a worldwide supplier of food 
and food ingredients including yeast cheese frozen potatoes and 
food colorings it employs about 4600 people 
